title: GoPro: Eddie Kelly Surfs the Crowds at Snapper Rocks
description:
Join Eddie Kelly at Snapper Rocks on the Gold Coast in Queensland, Australia as he gets a unique prospective inside the barrel. Eddie won Surfline's GoPro of the World contest for the month of February 2016 and takes home $1,000, a GoPro HERO4, and a year subscription to Surfline.

Shot 100% on the HERO4® camera 

Music

transcripts: My home break is Snapper rocks on the Gulf Coast in Australia,The way the sand lines up with the direction of the sell that comes around Create a wave that breaks to 3 kilometers I think that's why everybody travels here to try to get one of those perfect rides where you can get 20 seconds Barrels. It's a challenging wave with a big amount of people surfing. I got in with real good conditions 1 day and it all lined up.  [Music Playing]
